creator: Atlas Biomed Group Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
The AtlasHealth app is your health control centre, now always at hand. Manage your disease risks, follow the personal food recommendations and keep an eye on your sport-related characteristics. With Atlas, you are provided with the latest technologies so you can change for the better. Use the power of knowing your DNA and gut bacteria composition to stay healthy and happy.

MANAGING YOUR TESTS
Order the Atlas DNA and Microbiome test, track shipping status and receive your genetic data using your personal account in Atlas Biomed. Provided information depends on which set of tests you have passed.

RECOMMENDATIONS
Easy-to-follow instructions on your lifestyle, including the list of weekly Top 10 prebiotic foods to keep your gut healthy and food diary that helps keep track of how your diet changes the bacterial community with each meal (for the Atlas Microbiome test users).

HEALTH
Get to know your body’s strengths and weaknesses to manage the disease risks.
• Genetic risks of 21 chronic diseases
• Carrier status for 317 hereditary conditions
• The link between gut bacteria and common diseases

NUTRITION
Be aware how your body metabolism works to make better decisions about your diet
• Eating habits explained
• Vitamin and mineral levels impacted by genetics and gut bacteria
• Predisposition for some nutrients intolerances
• Microbiome diversity level

ANCESTRY
Get to know your roots from thousands of years ago
• Maternal and paternal haplogroups
• The route your ancestors travelled
• Ancestry composition based on more than 125 populations
• The ratio of neanderthal genes in your genome
• Nationality of your microbiome

SPORTS
(for the Atlas DNA test users)
Adjust your training plan according to your body metabolism
• Genetic predisposition to strength or endurance
• Risks of sport injuries

PERSONAL TRAITS
(for the Atlas DNA test users)
Iris structure, early grey hair or even whether you sneeze when suddenly exposed to sunlight – these are just some of the personal traits that we analyse.

About Atlas Biomed
Atlas Biomed is a personalised health company that combines DNA and microbiome technologies with digital health data to inspire people into a positive lifestyle change and lead them to a healthier future. Genetic data is analyzed in a certified EU laboratory in Denmark, accredited with ISO 17025.
descriptionShort: The AtlasHealth app is your health control centre, now always at hand.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Microbiome users, now you just need to snap pics of your meals with your smartphone to keep track of your diet! The rest is on us: our algorithm identifies the ingredients in each photo and gives you a score based on their benefits for your gut bacteria.

- Take a picture of your food
- Check the accuracy of ingredient recognition
- Get your score and feedback on the benefits of your diet for your microbiome

Happy to hear what you think of this update.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s new
We’ve made it even easier to complete your food diary: you can now search for meals by ingredient, and your meal entries can be amended for up to 24 hours.
A varied diet supports a healthy gut, but we’re also here to save you time. If you’re repeating a meal, you can now access your food history for the previous seven days and duplicate the entry in your food diary.
We would love to hear your experiences of this update, hit us up at hello@atlastbiomed.com
